trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of namespace objects.
trans-unit.target: 包含命名空間物件的集合。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceCollection> contains <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo> objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceCollection>包含<xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo>物件。

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo> object is the same as an `Import` (`<%@ Import %>`) directive that applies to all pages and controls in the scope of the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 每個<xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo>物件等同於`Import`(`<%@ Import %>`) 指示詞，可以套用到所有頁面，並控制在組態檔的範圍內。

trans-unit.source: The `Import` directive allows you to import a namespace into your ASP.NET page, making all its classes available for use on your page.
trans-unit.target: `Import`指示詞可讓您匯入到您的 ASP.NET 網頁，因此它的類別可以使用您的頁面上的命名空間。

trans-unit.source: The following configuration file excerpt shows how to declaratively specify values for several properties of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: 下列組態檔摘錄示範如何以宣告方式指定的數個屬性的值<xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceCollection>類別。

trans-unit.target: 將 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> 物件加入至集合。

trans-unit.source: The collection must not already contain a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo> object with the same <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo.Namespace%2A> property value.
trans-unit.target: 集合必須已經包含<xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo>物件具有相同<xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo.Namespace%2A>屬性值。

trans-unit.target: 要加入的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> 物件已經存在於集合中，或者集合是唯讀的。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that determines whether the Visual Basic namespace is imported without having to specify it.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定值，判斷是否不需要指定 Visual Basic 命名空間即可匯入它。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the Visual Basic namespace is imported automatically; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果會自動匯入 Visual Basic 命名空間，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: 預設值為 <see langword="true" />。

trans-unit.source: For ASP.NET pages written using Visual Basic the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic> namespace is automatically imported unless the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceCollection.AutoImportVBNamespace%2A> property is `false`.
trans-unit.target: 適用於使用 Visual Basic 撰寫的 ASP.NET 網頁<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic>命名空間會自動匯入，除非<xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceCollection.AutoImportVBNamespace%2A>屬性是`false`。

trans-unit.source: This method empties the collection and inserts a `clear` element into the appropriate section of the configuration file to remove all references to elements defined in higher-level configuration files and in the current configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會將集合清空，並將插入`clear`插入適當的區段中的組態檔，移除目前的設定檔和更高層級的組態檔中定義的項目的所有參考的項目。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> object at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定位於集合中所指定索引處的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> object at the specified index, or <see langword="null" /> if there is no object at that index.
trans-unit.target: 位於指定索引處的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> 物件；如果該索引處沒有任何物件，則為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: This property overwrites the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo> object if it already exists at the specified index; otherwise, a new object is created and added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 這個屬性會覆寫<xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo>物件已經存在指定的索引; 否則新的物件已建立，並加入至集合。

trans-unit.target: 要從集合中移除之 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> 物件的命名空間。

trans-unit.source: Removes the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> object with the specified key from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 移除集合中具有指定索引鍵的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: If the specified element is defined in a higher-level configuration file, this method inserts a `remove` element into the appropriate section of the configuration file at the level of the current application.
trans-unit.target: 如果在較高層級的組態檔中定義指定的項目，這個方法會插入`remove`插入適當的區段，在目前應用程式層級的組態檔項目。

trans-unit.source: If the element is defined in the current configuration file, its entry is removed from the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 如果目前的組態檔中定義的項目，其項目會從組態檔中移除。

trans-unit.source: The object to remove must exist in the collection; if it does not, a <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 要移除的物件必須存在於集合中，如果沒有，<xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationException>就會擲回。
